BUG + FIX: In Chromebook if I enable "Dark Backgrounds" in settings and close app and relaunch, the background will be Dark but the font will remain dark too. replyContent: It will only use American spellings if installed on a device configured to be in the US; you might want to check your phone location settings. On a standard phone configuration elsewhere it will show British English spellings.
